[VI] 1
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:05,500
[VI] -902, 0201... -There's no sign of the Hollows!

[VI] 2
00:00:05,500 --> 00:00:10,000
[VI] -The construction will be complete in a few days! -Captain, this is...

[VI] 3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:16,500
[VI] They're the only ones who can erase the Hollows from existence.

[VI] 4
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:20,500
[VI] I heard that the Hollows are more likely to appear in Karakura.

[VI] 5
00:00:20,500 --> 00:00:24,500
[VI] I was wondering if I was the only one who would come here.

[VI] 6
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:28,500
[VI] What a crowd!

[VI] 7
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:30,500
[VI] I can't face them like this.

[VI] 8
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:33,000
[VI] Who are you?

[VI] 9
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:35,000
[VI] Ichigo Kurosaki.

[VI] 10
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:37,000
[VI] I'm the Death God.

[VI] 11
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:42,000
[VI] -Sorry to keep you waiting! -I don't know who you are.

[VI] 12
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:45,500
[VI] -I don't know why you're attacking me. -Kurosaki, be careful.

[VI] 13
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:48,500
[VI] -Your opponent is... -It's a big problem!

[VI] 14
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,500
[VI] -It's Megaman! It's Megaman! -Yes, yes!

[VI] 15
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:58,000
[VI] The big selection tournament is about to begin!

[VI] 16
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:02,500
[VI] -You're the Queen City's... -Do you remember me? Ichigo Kurosaki.

[VI] 17
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:05,500
[VI] Everything that's happening now is connected.

[VI] 18
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:08,500
[VI] It's not just a coincidence.

[VI] 19
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:13,500
[VI] -So you know everything. -It's none of your business.

[VI] 20
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:18,000
[VI] I order all captains to prepare for battle.

[VI] 21
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:20,000
[VI] You damn Death Gods.

[VI] 22
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:25,500
[VI] I, Sternbitter, will purge you.

[VI] 23
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:30,000
[VI] -I understand. I'll go help you. -Let's do this.

[VI] 24
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:32,000
[VI] Bankai!

[VI] 25
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:38,000
[VI] Sorry, but I'm ordering you to kill everyone.

[VI] 26
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:41,500
[VI] -It's none of your business. -I'll beat you up.

[VI] 27
00:01:41,500 --> 00:01:46,000
[VI] -Your Bankai ends here! -Please, say something.

[VI] 28
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:50,500
[VI] -Sternbitter! -You have to endure it. Ichigo will come for you.

[VI] 29
00:01:50,500 --> 00:01:54,500
[VI] I won't let you die. I won't let you all die.

[VI] 30
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:59,000
[VI] I'll protect you!

[VI] 31
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:03,000
[VI] Sternbitter!

[VI] 32
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:12,500
[VI] Now, let's hear the news of peace.

[VI] 33
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:19,500
[VI] The power to crush fate is like a blade that can be swung down.

[VI] 34
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:23,500
[VI] Sternbitter!

[VI] 35
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:25,500
[VI] Sternbitter

